  <summary date="2020-07-30T13:42:27Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protecting Community Television Act

This bill revises the definition of a franchise fee that is paid by a cable operator or cable subscriber to encompass only a tax, fee, or other monetary assessment that is imposed by a franchising authority or other governmental entity.</summary>
